tafsir[15]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Alla woondirii hoodere sinde fukkiima."
  53,3,"O haalatah e o quraana tawa hombo rewi e belaaɗe makko."
  53,5,"Ko malayka jom semmbe oon woni Jibriil anndini ɗum mbo."
  53,7,"Jibriir hombo e jookli toowɗi."
  53,8,"Refti Jibriir ɓadii o ɓeydi ɓattaade."
  53,9,"O ɓadinoo mbo fotde laanye ɗiɗe wolla ko ɓuri ɓadaade."
  53,10,"Jibriir wahyii faade e maccuɗo Alla muhamadu-yo o his- ko O wahyii ko."
  53,11,"ɓernde muhamadu -yo o his- fennaani ko O yi*i ko."
  53,12,"mbela hoɗon njeddandira e makko-onon heefareeɓe-ko Alla holli mbo ko ñande jemma israa mbo Alla nawi mbo?"
  53,13,"Ko goonga tigi muhamadu-yo o his- yi*ii e mbaadi makko laawol goɗngol e jemma israa he."
  53,15,"ka kiin lekki woni aljanna koɗirɗo."
  53,19,"Mbela on nji*ii-onon heefereeɓe- sanamuuji ndewaton ɗi ko aldah e Alla:Laata e Ujjaa."
  53,20,"E manaata tatɓiija goɗɗo o e sanamuuji mon. kabree kam mbela hoɓe njoganii on nafoore wolla lorla."
  53,22,"Ndeen fecccoore nde peccirɗon belaaɗe mon ko nde tooñnde."
  53,24,"Mbela na woodani neɗɗa ko o wooɗa ko e tefnga sanamuuji faade Alla?"